---
title: Chipotle-Glazed Pork Chops with Garlic-Mashed Potatoes and Roasted Broccoli
description: The combination of floral honey and intense, smoky chipotle makes a delicious glaze for pan-seared pork chops. Roasting broccoli until golden brown brings out a delightfully nutty flavour. Paired with classic garlic-mashed potatoes, this is classic comfort food with a spicy twist.
